{"tid":1422564,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"八月十日 「守護孩子未來」親子集會","createTime":"2019-08-06T11:14:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T07:27:36.000Z","uid":186297,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"b4da516555529e7d691c02d8222b336a27968241","tid":1422564,"uid":186297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:14:49.000Z","msg":"輪到爸媽＋細路上場！sor遲左咁多！<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲同勇武努力左咁耐，受埋我地好喎！<br />\n<br />\n領住個細既係慢d同後d， <br />\n但有仔女既和理非會為下一代，係唔同層面同政府博到盡，向上一代解說。<br />\n<br />\n所以我們要集氣！幫個忙，傳俾身邊一家大細同文宣組！<br />\n<br />\n要政府回應5大訴求！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我們的初衷</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我們是一群香港的爸爸媽媽</span>，我們成長於香港，也在這個地方養育我們的下一代。作為父母，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我們一直努力地教導我們的孩子是與非、黑與白、對與錯，勇於承擔錯誤和責任</span></span>，讓他們成為一個好人，將來貢獻社會。 <br />\n<br />\n可是，近月逃犯修訂引起的風波和警民衝突升級，幕幕都<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">衝擊著孩子單純的心靈</span></span></span>：高官和警察公然說謊；警察以最高十年刑期的暴動罪檢控只是路過扶起跌倒士威者的情侶；白衣人拿著鐵通衝進車廂向市民施暴卻求助無門&hellip;&hellip;孩子對此可能感到莫名的恐懼和疑惑，父母亦不知道該如何向孩子解釋這些荒謬絕論的情況。而面對日益嚴厲的打壓。勿忘初心，讓我們建立一個安全的集會，表達父母和孩子的訴求。<br />\n<br />\n因此，<span style=\"color: pink;\">我們決定舉辦一個為家長和孩子度身訂造的集會及遊行</span>，希望家長可安心重新帶著孩子上路，向社會傳達我們對香港的<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">愛、未來、希望</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">「守護孩子未來」親子集會/遊行詳情：</span></span><br />\n日期：2019年8月10日（星期六）<br />\n時間：上午10點30分至至中午12點<br />\n集會地點：中環愛丁堡廣場 <br />\n遊行路線：中環愛丁堡廣場 至 政府總部<br />\n內容：DIY banner齊齊畫, 小小連儂人, 製作希望風車, 掛上願望氣球等<br />\n<br />\n行多步: <br />\n🎈自己物資自己帶！<br />\n＊基本野：地墊、水、小食、遮、防蚊設備<br />\n＊畫DIY banner：廣告彩顏料、畫筆、調色板、布碎<br />\n＊小小連儂人：不同顏色的postit、marker筆<br />\n＊製作希望風車：一隻木筷、一枝棉花棒（一隻風車）<br />\n<br />\n🎈Be River一領二，朋友仔撘朋友仔去，仲可以分開拿物資！<br />\n<br />\n＊不反對通知書申請進行中，將持續更新消息<br />\n特別留意星期五之公告<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/104332624250715/posts/105869067430404?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F104332624250715%2Fposts%2F105869067430404%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=Lhg6HStjEOrAYLon%2F%2F44J9%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=e8e606e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/104332624250715/posts/105869067430404?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"8def18cd8f8eab6e45b6757745c2aececa50054c","tid":1422564,"uid":186297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:16:01.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23c2aea686ad529b9273270d8e7a08d0b921d069","tid":1422564,"uid":29689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:16:05.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"8f3d7e58e36433b47f2b389fb234b8a8d970c7fc","tid":1422564,"uid":186297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:21:07.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無爸媽呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba4c3a17076865af5c13f254aae59f25997648d","tid":1422564,"uid":270910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:24:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d40a8ca0ed6371b3a6d7133bbacd26919e1835b1","tid":1422564,"uid":265555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:29:17.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b53249fb923f4fede6fb580a11f24bc2d0027c37","tid":1422564,"uid":282351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:29:48.000Z","msg":"好快要靠番d細路，早日傳承<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95e3900b334822991fed04987945d65d3e2271b7","tid":1422564,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:30:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94ae82dd3e4643b3e2140d249461d53ca15455d","tid":1