00 noon<br />\nVenue: Edinburgh Place, Central<br />\nRoute:  Edinburgh Place, Central to Government Headquarters<br />\n<br />\n*Letter of No Objection received.<br />\n<br />\nTelegram Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/childfuturehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fchildfuturehk&d=Lhg6HStjEOrAYLon%2F%2F44J9%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=477f8634\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/childfuturehk</a>"},{"pid":"81c06cc381c735549f05154ca72cb75f18fb0fd9","tid":1422564,"uid":182195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:48:10.000Z","msg":"推，明日就係"}]}